Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Excelsior Steel. So I'm wearing the body this morning it's a bit of a problem you just
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,have to be patient. Sometimes the condition is stronger than others and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to put up whatever is today. How many people are new today? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very easy to see that everything is happening spontaneously. That even your
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,thinkingness is happening all of its own. And you think that you're deciding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're going to think but you're not. So you get detached from your own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,thinkingness the same as the world. You see the world around you is moving
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,without your help. Right? All these people are managing to survive without you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,helping them to be here and move and talk. And so what you do is you get detached and you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,begin to become the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To become the witness is not a difficult step. It's only a matter of letting go the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,narcissistic self-indulgence of the thinking of that there's an I causing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,things. Nothing is causing anything. There are no causes in the world. There's only
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,consequences. And so what you do is you let go of identifying with the linear and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize that your reality is non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is witnessing and then behind that which is witnessing that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,aware that you're witnessing and already you've removed yourself from out there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and individual personal I and the guilt and anxiety of being the cause of all that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,happens and you've moved into this the condition of humility. With profound
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,humility you will see that you're not the cause of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is welcome news because that means you're also not guilty of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If something happens you say, I don't know the mind did it. I can't help it, the mind did it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To become the witness, then, you become aware then of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the spontaneity of evolution and you begin to witness all phenomena are the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolution of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation has a source but no cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no beginning and it has no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You witness the enfoldment of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no problem about creation because it's what you're witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that it's all happening spontaneously is not difficult to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not difficult to move from the participant subject out there, the linear,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and move into being the field out of which the phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you're being aware of the phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are is the field and not the content of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This observation escapes about 99% of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,99% is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At least 99% of humanity is completely unaware of what we're talking about this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not counting on widespread acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That you are the context rather than the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You are that from which awareness radiates and out of which consciousness arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The source is consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of God is consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the light of God is your own consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and as you let go
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,misidentifying with that which you are not
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes stunningly apparent
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,at which point you retire
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and they call the doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he's lost his wits
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that's true you do lose your wits
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes it's worse than others
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so today I am witless
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll have to put up with that condition
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,alright we always have some new people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so we do some review of some very basic things
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to start with what's new first
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and then move back to what you know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or do you want to start with what you know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to move to what's new
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,all the new people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you want what's new
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,start with what's new
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,then move to what's
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll do both
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,beginnings and ends are all in your head
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,they're in the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,we do start
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,just for orientation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with the calibrated map of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,as a common point of reference
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah friend
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's what we'll do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,start with that one
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and yes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,explain it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain it maybe a little bit differently
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,where's the first slide there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,where's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,there we go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll re-explain the map of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I went from one to a thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I went from one to a thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I went from one to a thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have gone from A to Z
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,because everybody thinks a number
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a higher number makes you better than other people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,no it doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it just means you're seeing things in a different light
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,blue green we could do it with colors
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've decided the best way to do it is with money
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so this calibration
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,here is not worth much money
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's worth a thousand dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're all trying for the job
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're all trying for the jackpot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so the lower levels of consciousness are just not worth much
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll only get you a few bomb loads of kids to blow up or something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing spectacular
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so we decided we'd change it to money
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and these are not worth much money down here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the exchange rate deepens
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it depends on the exchange rate
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the media have jacked up the exchange rate
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,which we'll get into later
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so that this now pays more than this up here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,oh god it's hysterical
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how the world survives
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and God tells me not to let on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so I won't
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ever have preachers God tells them this and God tells them that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd listen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hear silence
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the sound of God is silence
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates it a thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:10:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the sound of God is silence
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to have sound you have to have linearity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to have that which is sound and that which is not sound
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you have to give configuration to the sound
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore mantras and things and going oom and things
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,will take you to a certain level
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and beyond that you get you become aware of the silence behind the sound
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and so the purpose of the sound is to take you to the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why repeating a mantra repeatedly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,can sometimes really just lead to an altered state of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and the high feeling that you get disappears when you stop the mantra
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so they all have limited
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,limited
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,usages
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,there are cysts at certain points but you can't put your whole life
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,as a mantra
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you can put your whole life as a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,because a prayer is a verbalization of a nonlinear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,intentionality
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of prayer to make your life a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to become that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to become that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which you are speaks louder than what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,essence speaks louder than perception
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,which we'll get to later
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so that's the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels of consciousness as I said
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it's relatively well known
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it was an arbitrary scale
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because we needed some way to refer to it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's also logarithmic so that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as you go up the numbers increase very very rapidly
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why we use logarithms
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,very very rapidly
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,alright now what did I say was the next slide after that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,any questions on the calibrated level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,as I say it doesn't say that you're better than others
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not a matter of better
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because our status oriented
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,society
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:11:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we say it's better
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not better
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it's different than
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,different than
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and very often to be in a different than
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,state of consciousness that is not appropriate to where you are
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be a hindrance you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to be blissed out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you know when you're driving is not so great
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to pull over
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so you have to sort of be in what's appropriate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but that begins to adjust itself automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is true that if you suddenly advance to a high state
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you may be quite incapacitated
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's well to have spiritual friends
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,hang out with spiritual people
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual friends
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and you let them know that you're
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you know seriously studying etc
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you go into such states
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,they will recognize what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and that was a function I used to have
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Zen Monastery back east
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a consultant to the Episcopal Diocese
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the Catholic Diocese
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the Ministerial Council
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the Zen Monastery
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and they would bring in people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and is he catatonic or is he in Samadhi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,they didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and because they would go into a silent still state
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,which is not dissimilar from catatonia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,which I used to see in the hospital you know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I told you that story
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a catatonic that hadn't spoken in 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and they would put his hand up like this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and he would stay that way year in and year out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,not move
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,he would have to move his hand down like that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and one time he saw the head of the hospital coming
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and the nurses weren't supposed to smoke or drink coffee in the office
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and he saw them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,he hadn't spoken in 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden he turned and he said
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Travis
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the nurses put their coffee in there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the only thing he ever said
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:14:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Travis is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,unbelievable
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they had to tube feed him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,he wouldn't eat you know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,catatonia
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so in a high bliss state
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it might be difficult to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is this person catatonic
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,or in a high state of bliss
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and without calibrating them you can't tell
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so the value of this discovery of course
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,my interest was in sharing it with the world
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you know why I teach is the same reason
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fleming
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ran around after he discovered penicillin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you know he discovered penicillin accidentally
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,just as I discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the basis of how we discern truth from falsehood
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,was a chance observation
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,which I got in an instant what it signified
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and Fleming discovered the same thing with the petri dish
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,when he noticed that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the moles had
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,killed off the bacteria
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,oh my god
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,he got what it meant you see
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,one thing to see it is another to get what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and Fleming got what it meant
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,oh my god he got what it meant
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and then by experimentation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he discovered penicillin
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course it's a whole new era
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,those amongst us who are doctors remember
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the days when everybody was dying of typhoid
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and malaria and polio and tuberculosis
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the terrible diseases which no longer even exist
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't even see these illnesses anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's transformed the world antibiotics
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and so what Fleming was interested in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was the importance of discovery
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and he couldn't get anybody to listen to it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because it was coming from a different context
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and he ran around for some five years
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody would listen to him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then in World War II
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the combatants of course had injuries
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the soldiers and sailors
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,had injuries so
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,wound injuries the infections
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the infection was what
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,finally killed you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the infection was the main thing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you got a bullet through the arm
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say it was nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because I've had similar things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not nothing but
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what kills you then was the bacterial infection
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,six weeks later
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you had six weeks of high fever
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and various things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so what Fleming's motivation was
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to share this with the world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was only because of the military's need
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in World War II
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that some of the military
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the army finally listened to him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and we now have the whole era
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of antibiotics and pharmaceuticals
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's the motivation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,about writing the books
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and about giving the lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is I know what the catalytic value
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of the information is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and my intention is to share that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,sufficiently widely that it radiates
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own henceforth
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's why we're here today
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so we'll go on then
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll go on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,oh yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,well we want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,not the obligations of spiritual teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but I want to have
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,characteristics
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we want characteristics of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,we want
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,thirty nine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,thirty nine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we want thirty nine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,can we get thirty nine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we've done this slide before
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but because of various things
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that come into the office
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,between lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize that I may not have explained
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,certain things adequately
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,by the style of the question
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,all truth is truth everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,under all conditions throughout all time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,truth is different from a fact
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact is linear
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,definable
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,confirmable
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,truth is essence
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,truth is essence
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and the majority of people have no way of discerning truth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,from falsehood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so the alignment of the spiritual teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is to share
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,truth which is a universal truth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not exclusive
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's available to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,available to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the integrity of the purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing to gain or lose
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not sectarian
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it's independent of opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,now truth is quite different from opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of times people will
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you know write and say
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,how come you said
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you said so and so
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates a so and so
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,they presume there's a you though that said that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,there isn't any you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,much less did that you say anything
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:18:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a measurement
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,like a barometric pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,or an altitude
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it just calibrates at a certain thing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we're talking today about you know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,differentiating perception from
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,reality
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it's devoid of a position
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,has no requirements or demands
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't charge you know a monthly fee
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,now you can get on the internet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,for a fee you can get enlightened in 30 days
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,60 days or 90 days
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,depending on which one you sign up for
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't be done
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't be done
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate the spirit in which
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it's presented to the world but
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it could take many a lifetime you know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't really even by coaching
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,get somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and their way to full enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,what I call in the writings the final door
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is at $9.99
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not at $5.99
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,there's some
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,teaching out there it's at $5.99
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a misunderstanding
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,$5.99 is just before
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you hit $600 which is bliss
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,bliss sat in
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,sat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,chitinanda
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the bliss state is at $600
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,one of infinite peace
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and it comes right after the ecstatic phase
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the final doorway is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,$9.99
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that is a whole different thing altogether
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tegra's teaching is that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't really sign people up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and charge them
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and guarantee that you're going to raise
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,their level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple times a day
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're going to be enlightened in 30 or 60 or 90 days
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't be done
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what it does is appeal to the spiritual ego
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibrated numbers therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual ego will instantly get attracted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to want to be better
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and calibrate higher
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the doorway into heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't have a book of calibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Peter doesn't say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you calibrated 422
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,well you got to go to that heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you calibrated that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,each of us has an essence
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that essence automatically gravitates
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which it is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which it is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,don't worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrating higher
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the purposes of the lecture overall
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,from a strictly spiritual viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have two levels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,one is scientific
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,as a clinician
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize the benefit
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in many many fields
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of being able to tell truth from falsehood
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean the world hasn't even
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,glimpsed it yet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what can be done with that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:22:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's the scientific viewpoint then
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time in history
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you can differentiate truth from falsehood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,not only that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.41,0:22:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but the level of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,which tells you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,what paradigm of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,because most confusion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is a confusion of paradigms
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,one speaking from this paradigm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the main one in our world today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in America
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.41,0:22:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is the dispute between
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness levels below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.41,0:22:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,with those above 200
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it's really almost like
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,two different societies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and worldwide
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the same conditions are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,war between
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that which calibrates below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with that which calibrates above 200
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so it doesn't make you better than
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but it does put you in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a different crowd of people
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,an integrity spiritual group
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is very supportive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't necessarily need
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,their physical appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the minute you are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:22:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you are in your own mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,part of that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.93,0:23:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,then you pick up the energy of that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and then when you decline that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you lose the energy of that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say that the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,are not supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,controlling people
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,not having any requirements
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,or demands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you got to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,no oaths
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,no requirements
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,no dues
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to sign up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,for anything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.41,0:23:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,next thing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,what goes after 10
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,11
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,well that's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we might as well restate
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual teacher then
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because there seems to be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.43,0:23:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,a great many
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.43,0:23:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm somewhat disquieted
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.46,0:23:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when I calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,some of the better known
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.55,0:23:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that the fallout
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is quite considerable
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:23:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I consider it the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:23:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:23:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of those teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:23:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to have
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,forewarned them
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of what the temptations are
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because they have
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.16,0:24:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,fell innocently into it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.16,0:24:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the narcissistic core
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.25,0:24:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is in direct competition with God
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.25,0:24:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and the more godly you get
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.25,0:24:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the more
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.25,0:24:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the more clever it gets
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.25,0:24:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.25,0:24:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.50,0:24:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,ah
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.50,0:24:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,what
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.33,0:24:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,oh
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.06,0:24:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,she skipped
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.06,0:24:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,okay well
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.06,0:24:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.06,0:24:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.06,0:24:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,non-binding
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.14,0:24:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to sign up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.14,0:24:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,for anything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.14,0:24:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you're free to come and go
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.14,0:24:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,without a rattlesnake
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.14,0:24:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,being put in your mailbox
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.14,0:24:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it's inspiration
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.53,0:24:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.53,0:24:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't see
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.53,0:24:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,glamorization
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.53,0:24:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,seduction
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.53,0:24:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and theatrics
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.53,0:24:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so when we go over
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.53,0:24:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,this list
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.53,0:24:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.53,0:24:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the list of fallen gurus
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.53,0:24:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,which I won't
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.53,0:24:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,once presented
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.53,0:24:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and it costs so much
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.53,0:24:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,clamor
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.53,0:24:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can decide not to do it again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.53,0:24:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.98,0:24:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it's because of being
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.98,0:25:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled into those things
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.98,0:25:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,being pulled into
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.98,0:25:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.98,0:25:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the glamour
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.98,0:25:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and the theatrics
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.98,0:25:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.04,0:25:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.04,0:25:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the theatre
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.04,0:25:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.04,0:25:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,drama
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.04,0:25:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.04,0:25:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.04,0:25:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,endemic in certain regions
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.04,0:25:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.36,0:25:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.36,0:25:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.49,0:25:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it's detached
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.49,0:25:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,from trying to control
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.49,0:25:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,things out there
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.49,0:25:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it's benign
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.49,0:25:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.49,0:25:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it's self-fulfilling
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.49,0:25:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not intentional
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.57,0:25:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.43,0:25:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is there such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.43,0:25:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as a purpose though
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.43,0:25:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.55,0:25:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,as I said
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.66,0:25:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.66,0:25:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,two motives
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.66,0:25:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,one is to share
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.66,0:25:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what I think is beneficial
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.75,0:25:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.75,0:25:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other is
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.75,0:25:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,by using that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.75,0:25:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,which is beneficial
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.75,0:25:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to delineate
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.75,0:25:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,a clear path
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.75,0:25:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,through what the world
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.75,0:25:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,has classically called
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.75,0:25:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.75,0:25:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.84,0:25:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,realization of the self
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.84,0:25:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,god consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.84,0:25:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever name
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.84,0:25:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you want to call it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.84,0:25:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.84,0:25:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,just the progressive
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.88,0:25:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,disidentification
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.88,0:25:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with the linear
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.88,0:25:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.88,0:25:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,be realizing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.88,0:26:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.91,0:26:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the non-linear
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.91,0:26:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you're the field
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.91,0:26:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in which
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.91,0:26:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the linear mind
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.91,0:26:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,operates
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.91,0:26:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,if it wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.91,0:26:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,for the field
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.91,0:26:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.91,0:26:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,what your linear mind
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.91,0:26:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.91,0:26:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.91,0:26:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the light
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.91,0:26:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that lights up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.91,0:26:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.91,0:26:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,lights up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.91,0:26:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind itself
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.91,0:26:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so you know
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.91,0:26:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,what the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.91,0:26:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.91,0:26:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.91,0:26:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so then
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.25,0:26:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll move on
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.25,0:26:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to the next one
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.25,0:26:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.45,0:26:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,there's an inner
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.45,0:26:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,tranquility
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.45,0:26:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and peace
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.45,0:26:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,equality
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.45,0:26:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.48,0:26:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,non-temporality
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.48,0:26:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.48,0:26:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.48,0:26:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond proof
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.48,0:26:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond proof
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.53,0:26:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.67,0:26:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.67,0:26:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,which we'll get
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.67,0:26:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to later
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.74,0:26:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.74,0:26:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,thrust
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.74,0:26:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in academia
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.74,0:26:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.79,0:26:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Daniel Dennett
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.79,0:26:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,people of that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.79,0:26:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,caliber
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.79,0:26:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.79,0:26:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,who would like
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.79,0:26:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to see
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.79,0:26:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dennett
