Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.82,0:53:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,God doing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.82,0:53:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.82,0:53:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,God just sits there
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.07,0:53:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you do it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.07,0:53:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.61,0:53:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,God has always
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.61,0:53:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,been the big cop out
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.78,0:54:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.78,0:54:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,an angry God
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.78,0:54:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,who punishes you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.78,0:54:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,etc
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.78,0:54:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.78,0:54:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,by your own
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.78,0:54:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,choice
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.78,0:54:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and selection
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.78,0:54:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you put yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.78,0:54:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.78,0:54:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,or hell
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.09,0:54:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and the consequences
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.09,0:54:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then are up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.09,0:54:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so the anthropomorphic
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.09,0:54:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,God
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.09,0:54:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.09,0:54:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,with the atheist
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.09,0:54:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the anthropomorphic
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.09,0:54:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,God
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.09,0:54:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.09,0:54:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,with the atheist
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.09,0:54:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.09,0:54:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,with the atheist
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.09,0:54:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,by the way
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.09,0:54:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I do believe
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.09,0:54:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in the next
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.73,0:54:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,tract
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.73,0:54:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we're in
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.73,0:54:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.73,0:54:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we need
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.73,0:54:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to be
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.73,0:54:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.73,0:54:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,mass
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.78,0:54:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,medium
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.73,0:54:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,if
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.73,0:54:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.73,0:54:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.86,0:54:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.86,0:54:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,plant
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.86,0:54:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but as a consequence of what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.51,0:54:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what you are, your essence that radiates out
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.53,0:54:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and lifts the sea of all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.76,0:55:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, what can I do to benefit mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.38,0:55:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay home.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.46,0:55:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay home. Keep out of traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.80,0:55:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And purify yourself via all the spiritual tools that you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.86,0:55:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of just talking about them and having parades about them,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.69,0:55:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.86,0:55:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.30,0:55:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the speed of the evolution of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.09,0:55:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You see man is in a very rampant up thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.61,0:55:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever that is. Move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.61,0:55:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And for those that are new, we recapitulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.61,0:55:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The evolution of consciousness throughout all of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.63,0:55:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're driving, but we eventually get to some place
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.84,0:55:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,where we're going to go with these lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.84,0:55:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The nature of the ego itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.42,0:56:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to see that intrinsically,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.42,0:56:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego has to be what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.34,0:56:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when life emerged,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.26,0:56:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,back here some age too long ago to remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.09,0:56:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.23,0:56:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,animal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.03,0:56:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is not provided with the inner source of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.94,0:56:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the basic conflict of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.78,0:56:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,From Iraq to everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.36,0:56:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Man is lacking an inner source of protoplasmic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.75,0:56:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, as I always say,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.38,0:56:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the plants have chlorophyll.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.69,0:56:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have to kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.19,0:56:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have to conquer anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.03,0:56:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All they have to do is be.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.01,0:56:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And they survive as a consequence of that which they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.90,0:56:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not capable of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.05,0:56:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're blessed in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.17,0:56:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the animal, unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.23,0:56:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,lacks energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.21,0:56:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,has to constantly acquire.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.11,0:56:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego, therefore, is acquisitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.69,0:56:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to sample everything out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.86,0:57:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.69,0:57:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.42,0:57:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That which doesn't have an ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.67,0:57:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,animals without an ego don't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.67,0:57:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't tell what's poison and what's food,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.46,0:57:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't survive to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.05,0:57:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.80,0:57:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we evolve as animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.71,0:57:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,evolve then with an acquisition system.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.07,0:57:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the leading edge of the ego called the processor.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.59,0:57:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The processor is that leading edge of information,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.76,0:57:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,knowingness, gatheringness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.59,0:57:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It then organizes it as memory and intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.00,0:57:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the intelligent design of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.50,0:57:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Intelligent design of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.51,0:57:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It processes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.11,0:57:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And it has to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.40,0:57:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And those who are not capable of that die.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.55,0:57:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the ego is then,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.55,0:57:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is considered to be the source of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.11,0:57:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of life is that capacity to,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.98,0:58:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, sample by either perception or essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.90,0:58:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, once you get to the level where we're at in evolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.28,0:58:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it becomes important to know that we're seeing perception and essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.15,0:58:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the world doesn't know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.09,0:58:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The world thinks perception is essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.53,0:58:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the evolution of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.92,0:58:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness, then, means that the formation,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.11,0:58:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the acquisitive formation,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.07,0:58:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the idea that it is the source of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.73,0:58:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the guarantor of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.59,0:58:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And, therefore, we assume it is the source of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.46,0:58:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the narcissistic core of the ego is a natural,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.96,0:58:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,comes out of the nature of evolution itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.84,0:58:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And, unfortunately, in some people,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.57,0:58:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it does not become dominated by spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.28,0:58:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And, it continues on,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.73,0:58:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in which conquering triumphalism becomes an end in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.30,0:59:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what does this country have to conquer this country for?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.55,0:59:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it going to get more buses?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.61,0:59:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.61,0:59:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.61,0:59:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you see, history is just one country going in to conquer
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.61,0:59:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and get control of others, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.61,0:59:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, nowadays, we have oil, so it makes some kind of sense, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.13,0:59:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's the evolution of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.13,0:59:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.13,0:59:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And, we see the evolution through the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.19,0:59:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason I show the animal kingdom is because it demonstrates
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.19,0:59:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that evolution continues on through all of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.19,0:59:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,humankind, animal kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.19,0:59:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And, when it reaches a level of 200, it changes its nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.19,0:59:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It changes from violent and aggressive,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.40,0:59:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and it starts to become more benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.40,0:59:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you see at level 200, these animals are benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.42,0:59:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A deer won't attack you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.42,1:00:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, most of these people won't attack you,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.42,1:00:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you push them around a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.94,1:00:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a giraffe mad at you, but he doesn't want to be bothered,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.94,1:00:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.94,1:00:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway, then we get up to the dogs and the cats and the African grey,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.00,1:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and the African greys are a very interested parrot.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.00,1:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know all that there is to know about a parrot.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.00,1:00:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something there unknown.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.09,1:00:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And, the same with the cat's purr.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.38,1:00:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And, the dog's wagging tail.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.38,1:00:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's things we don't know about them.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.48,1:00:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And, a lot of times, we've asked at a lecture,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.48,1:00:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and we found out you weren't allowed to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.48,1:00:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't allowed to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.48,1:00:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.73,1:00:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the bird at home will ring the phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.73,1:00:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm busy now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.73,1:00:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.73,1:00:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.73,1:00:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.73,1:00:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Has a phone call on both ends.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.96,1:00:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Says hello and goodbye in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.96,1:00:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Has a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.96,1:01:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All by herself, sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.36,1:01:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, there's got to be something more to this that we're not seeing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.36,1:01:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would this be?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.55,1:01:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would this be?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.55,1:01:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It lives to be a hundred years of collecting all this information.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.55,1:01:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.09,1:01:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's got to be some purpose to the animal world that we haven't discovered as yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.09,1:01:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't discovered as yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.13,1:01:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember during some lectures we asked about the dog's wagging tail
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.13,1:01:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and the kitty's purr,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.13,1:01:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and we got to know we couldn't go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.13,1:01:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.13,1:01:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.13,1:01:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.13,1:01:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Move on to the next information here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.13,1:01:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is just a quick review because today we're going to talk about reason versus truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.86,1:01:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, what we find out is that truth is different calibrations.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.86,1:01:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's true here is not true here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.86,1:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not true here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.86,1:01:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One man, civilization, western civilization, is considered to be truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.44,1:02:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty much represented by the great books of the western world.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.44,1:02:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.44,1:02:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Which the greatest thinkers of all time.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.44,1:02:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The greatest thinkers that have influenced all of western society.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.44,1:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All of western society.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.44,1:02:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've spoken of many of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.44,1:02:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've spoken of the downside, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.44,1:02:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We've talked about dialectical materialism as being really the only one that's really out of there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.44,1:02:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think they made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.44,1:02:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Engels is right at 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.44,1:02:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But the University of Chicago dons with this together.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.44,1:02:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it included Freud as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.44,1:02:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud is at 499.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.44,1:02:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a great thinker.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.44,1:02:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And he belongs there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.44,1:02:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think they put him in Marx because of his importance in history.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.80,1:02:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Importance in history.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.80,1:02:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.80,1:02:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.80,1:02:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted us to look at it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.80,1:02:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking today about the content, which is in here, and context, which is out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.86,1:03:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can look at context as the infinite ultimate context, which we mean by calibration level.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.86,1:03:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond 1,000 is the infinite, and it goes on to infinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.86,1:03:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's experiential within the human domain up to level 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.86,1:03:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So here is the event and the situation in which it happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.86,1:03:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's the society in which you live.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.86,1:03:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's the field of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.86,1:03:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you identify with then, the meaning of the content, depends on the context.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.88,1:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll move on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.88,1:03:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Content is linear, the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.96,1:03:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's definable, Newtonian.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.96,1:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.96,1:03:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The proximate field, we'd say, would be the spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.36,1:03:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Current circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.36,1:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Quantum mechanics is the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.40,1:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the infinite context is spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.40,1:04:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.40,1:04:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's knowable.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.40,1:04:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's experiential.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.40,1:04:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ego and the self, the small s, is concerned and identifies with content, which is linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.59,1:04:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The self with a capital S, the background field out of which all knowingness arises, then is consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.15,1:04:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.38,1:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go on to the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.38,1:04:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So this morning we're doing a quick review.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.38,1:04:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, as I said this morning, this is very easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.38,1:04:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a spiritual student, you should be able to make this jump without much difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.38,1:04:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,30, 40, 50 years, you'll make it just like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.69,1:04:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you're in a hypnotic condition attracted by form.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.69,1:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch people when they walk into the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.69,1:04:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If the TV's on, their attention instantly goes to the form.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.69,1:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.69,1:05:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The new drapes are not what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.88,1:05:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The new rug is not what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.88,1:05:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening is some idiot face talking there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.88,1:05:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The person's like, oink.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.40,1:05:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You want the TV to own your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.40,1:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.40,1:05:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You want the TV to dominate your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.40,1:05:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.40,1:05:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the mind is attracted to form and action.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.40,1:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And it registers that with recognition.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.40,1:05:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, behind that, why is the TV interesting?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.67,1:05:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's the experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.67,1:05:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiencer says, I don't want to experience nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.75,1:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to experience something.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.78,1:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Better anything than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.78,1:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And many people will do anything rather than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.78,1:05:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.53,1:05:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because they don't like doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.53,1:05:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how to like doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.63,1:06:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to the watcher, the experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.63,1:06:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can move into the observer witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.63,1:06:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the observer witness that is not difficult to move into.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.76,1:06:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To realize that you're the witness of what you're experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.15,1:06:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know what you're experiencing?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.15,1:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's a witness, a watcher, an observer.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.15,1:06:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can realize that that which is unchanging is that you're always observing whether the TV's on or not on.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.40,1:06:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If the TV's not on, then you're enjoying the sound of the TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.82,1:06:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're enjoying the sound of the breeze.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.82,1:06:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.82,1:06:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If the TV's on, you're listening to the sound of the TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.82,1:06:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's always the watcher witness remains the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.26,1:06:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't care what's on the set.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.48,1:06:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can move back from identifying with the content to that which is the observer witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.94,1:06:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The observer witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.90,1:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you find that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.90,1:07:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.00,1:07:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you meditate or look within yourself, you'll see that observing and witnessing is happening all the time without your permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.00,1:07:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.32,1:07:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is your own condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.32,1:07:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The condition of being alive as a human being is to be the witness observer.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.32,1:07:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only commonality.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.32,1:07:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,People experience what they witness and observe differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.32,1:07:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But what they have in common is that they're all observing and witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.48,1:07:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the commonality of all humans.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.48,1:07:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As you're witnessing and observing and experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.48,1:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll figure out later how to get behind this.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.69,1:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So the observer witness then.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.69,1:07:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You become aware the observer and the witness are happening of their own.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.69,1:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Becoming aware.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.59,1:07:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As you sit in the audience right now, the being aware is happening of your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.59,1:08:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's a given.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.59,1:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.59,1:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are then is the consciousness itself out of which the observer witness arises.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.59,1:08:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we supposed to take a break this morning from that?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.78,1:08:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.94,1:08:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.94,1:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, see that?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.93,1:08:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What I need to know arises.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.93,1:08:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.93,1:08:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy Spirit keeps track of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.93,1:08:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Does all kinds of things for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.93,1:08:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As you get older, you don't remember things as well as you used to when you were younger.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.13,1:08:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for the Holy Spirit, I wouldn't know where I can put my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.13,1:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.22,1:08:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a constant miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.22,1:08:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget where I just laid something down.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.86,1:08:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, let's see, okay, uh-huh, uh-huh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.86,1:08:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember where the hell I laid it down because I'm not tracking things linearly.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.11,1:08:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So I go to the nonlinear source of all knowingness and I say, Holy Spirit, where did I leave the thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.51,1:09:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I walk right over and there it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.51,1:09:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.51,1:09:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't go an hour without the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.53,1:09:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.53,1:09:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.76,1:09:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You become more and more reliant and realize that it is the light of consciousness out of which your knowingness and your survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.76,1:09:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And the nature, the divine nature of that reveals itself as you remove the obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.97,1:09:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll move on to the next where I want to get all of it done this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.52,1:09:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This I'm going to just flash on quickly is very profound.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.52,1:09:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, there's really two civilizations sharing this planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.52,1:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Those above 200 and those below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.52,1:09:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my word for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.52,1:09:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two different civilizations.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.52,1:09:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't, by apology, fool yourself that they're the same as you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.52,1:09:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.52,1:09:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not the same as you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.06,1:09:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So Pollyanna will not get you to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.06,1:10:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, apologies for that which is not like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.11,1:10:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they not like you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.64,1:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because their brains work differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.64,1:10:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Politics isn't going to change that, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.80,1:10:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all the holy selling politics.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.39,1:10:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.39,1:10:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand-wringing and all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.39,1:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.34,1:10:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200, you see how their brain processes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.34,1:10:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the animal instinctual brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.34,1:10:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominance.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.34,1:10:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tribalism.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.34,1:10:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.34,1:10:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.63,1:10:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominate.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.63,1:10:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Revenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.23,1:10:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Get even.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.23,1:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rip.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.32,1:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tear.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.32,1:10:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.32,1:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.32,1:10:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.81,1:10:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an animal instinct.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.57,1:10:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes out of the left brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.57,1:10:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It dominates consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.57,1:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It dominates consciousness level below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.80,1:10:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness level 200 may be trained socially not to act it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.80,1:10:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But it thinks that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.15,1:11:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It thinks, I'd like to kill the son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.15,1:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.64,1:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.64,1:11:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.23,1:11:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here not wanting to kill that SOB?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.97,1:11:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.97,1:11:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.97,1:11:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't become spiritually evolved if you haven't wanted to kill somebody.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.97,1:11:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.97,1:11:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you have to care enough about life to get there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.97,1:11:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to care enough about life to get there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.27,1:11:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.27,1:11:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So congratulate yourself that you care enough about life to be indignant.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.27,1:11:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you'd be an apathetic whop.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.26,1:11:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A wet rag.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.26,1:11:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.93,1:11:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to care enough about it to give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.93,1:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can evolve to the point where you don't give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.38,1:11:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point, you turn the world over to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.61,1:11:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you realize the world is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.61,1:11:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You just didn't notice it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.61,1:11:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.61,1:11:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.61,1:12:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to finish this before our break.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.61,1:12:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 200, this side of the brain shoots in.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.61,1:12:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of putting out adrenaline, it puts out endorphins.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.61,1:12:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It puts out, what is it, oxytocin, the maternal hormone.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.61,1:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Without that hormone, people are not sociable.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.90,1:12:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that we're sociable and nice is due to the fact the brain produces a hormone that's
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.90,1:12:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,characteristic of pregnancy, oxytocin.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.90,1:12:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.35,1:12:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So the other culture, then, is operating in a different brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.14,1:12:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,These people have a different brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.14,1:12:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You people have a different brain than the other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.14,1:12:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you understand them, but you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.92,1:12:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.92,1:12:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I kid you so.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.92,1:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To screw you out of a buck is a sign of honor in that society.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.75,1:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To not screw you out of a buck is a sign of shame.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.75,1:12:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You came home.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.64,1:13:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How much did you get for the rug?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.64,1:13:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,$50.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.64,1:13:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a beating.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.64,1:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only worth $25.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.47,1:13:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have gotten $100.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.92,1:13:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To not be dishonest.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.92,1:13:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.92,1:13:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.92,1:13:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can see the difficulty the world has.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.92,1:13:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because these people are operating on a different side of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.96,1:13:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what it's willing to die for on the top there, conquering other people, getting
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.96,1:13:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,even.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.96,1:13:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what they're willing to die for.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.96,1:13:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only 200 and up now.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.96,1:13:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's because the Kundalini energy rises and shifts the brain dominance.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.96,1:13:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain now, instead of putting out emergency emotion hormones, kill or be killed, puts
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.97,1:13:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,out benevolence.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.97,1:13:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The hormones of benevolence.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.84,1:14:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, to understand the people, you have to understand that they're operating with
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.51,1:14:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,a different brain than you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.51,1:14:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you make them wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.51,1:14:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.51,1:14:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only make them wrong if they were the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.51,1:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have an option.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.51,1:14:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They see the world differently, experience it, value it differently, and therefore they're
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.51,1:14:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,doing what they should be doing as a good animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.98,1:14:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a good animal, you're supposed to be killing the other wolves to become the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.98,1:14:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,alpha male.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.98,1:14:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a son of a bitch as an alpha male.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.30,1:14:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.35,1:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Went for the jugular.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.35,1:14:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.35,1:14:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fast too.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.86,1:14:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I was a fly weight, a mosquito weight.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.86,1:14:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a living little terror.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.86,1:14:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A 90 pounds of .
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.96,1:14:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned if he hits you once, you're going to be out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.73,1:14:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd stay away from getting hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.73,1:14:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just got in there so fast they didn't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.77,1:14:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And they had a bloody nose and they went home crying to their mother and I won.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.77,1:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When I did get hit, I would get knocked out every time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.13,1:15:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I quit getting hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.13,1:15:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's time for a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.86,1:15:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a what?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.86,1:15:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,15 minute break?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.86,1:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.86,1:15:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No laughing during that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.11,1:15:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.11,1:15:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even have a sip of Diet Pepsi.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.72,1:15:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I did that whole spiel without the Diet Pepsi.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.72,1:15:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da.
